data.description: This beautiful home is nestled in the Woodland Pines Community near US-59/69.Brick & Cement siding two story with close to 3000 sq. ft.  Five ample bedrooms starting with first floor Master Suite.  Three and a half baths. New Neutral tile flooring throughout first floor, new carpet upstairs, fresh paint throughout this wonderful house. First floor: Formal Dining, Private Study,Kitchen, Family room with gas log fireplace.  Game Room upstairs. Two of the 4 upstairs bedrooms have Jack & Jill bath.  Gas range, separate laundry room and half bath downstairs.  Fully fenced back yard.  Easy access to Beltway 8, US69/59, Bush Airport, restaurants, stores.  Woodland Pines Subdivision has swimming pool and playground park.
